Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.85,0:00:07.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫雪村葵 今天開始就是高中生了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.31,0:00:11.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上了高中 也要一個人玩得高高興興！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.52,0:00:18.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小葵好久不見！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.12,0:00:20.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小學畢業第一次見面呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.58,0:00:21.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這誰來著
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.37,0:00:30.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,登山少女 BEST 10
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.63,0:00:33.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.46,0:00:35.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是主持人 久米日向
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.22,0:00:36.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白柳葵
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.76,0:00:41.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葵小姐 登山少女 BEST 10 終於開播了呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.48,0:00:42.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.84,0:00:46.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛大家看到的是 第10位 再會
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.52,0:00:49.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時候真沒看出來是誰呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.76,0:00:54.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上了高中 心氣太高了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.79,0:00:59.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本期節目將會回顧一下登山少女裏的經典片段
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.65,0:01:01.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來是BEST 10中第9位
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.23,0:01:08.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第9位 棉花糖少女可可娜醬
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.80,0:01:10.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnsimsun\shad0\bord3\3c&H000000&\blur4\pos(896,560)\c&HF1EFED&}天狗坐的杉樹
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.64,0:01:12.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於來到了高尾山
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.87,0:01:22.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鼯鼠先生 你在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.61,0:01:25.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在嗎…在嗎……
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.60,0:01:27.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是鼯鼠先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.87,0:01:36.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天狗先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.39,0:01:42.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 天狗先生
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.31,0:01:47.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天狗先生
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.83,0:01:48.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼！？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.71,0:02:02.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天狗先生 抓到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.55,0:02:05.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.85,0:02:12.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天…天狗先生……
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.09,0:02:20.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,森林裏的森林少女！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.72,0:02:24.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鞋底開膠了…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.06,0:02:30.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可可娜啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.21,0:02:37.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 竟然把天狗當成鼯鼠了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.31,0:02:40.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前的可可娜醬真是天然呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.78,0:02:41.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.01,0:02:43.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.02,0:02:47.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來 從第8位到第5位 一口氣看完吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.97,0:02:54.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第8位 我是小葵 小葵是我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.39,0:02:57.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可可娜醬再見啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.36,0:02:57.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.05,0:02:58.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.35,0:03:02.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.85,0:03:03.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圓點的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.09,0:03:05.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩 圓點的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.48,0:03:06.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圓點！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.21,0:03:08.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日向！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.80,0:03:09.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.40,0:03:13.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天絕饒不了你！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.20,0:03:14.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有啥啊 又沒掉塊肉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.38,0:03:18.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香蕉皮！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.62,0:03:22.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小葵學姐 日向學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.74,0:03:28.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.77,0:03:31.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日向你怎麼搞的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.07,0:03:35.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 都怪香蕉皮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.40,0:03:37.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.95,0:03:40.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日向你怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.56,0:03:42.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 我的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.40,0:03:46.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是晴天
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.58,0:03:48.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聲音怎麼這麼怪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.26,0:03:50.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的聲音變成小葵的聲音了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.05,0:03:53.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼賠我啊 都怪你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.75,0:03:56.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不知道呢 我也不想要這麼怪的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.91,0:03:59.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我的萌音還給我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.63,0:04:01.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完了嫁不出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.16,0:04:04.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 其實也不覺得怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.51,0:04:06.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.27,0:04:07.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒啥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.47,0:04:08.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩 沒啥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.82,0:04:09.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒啥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.28,0:04:12.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們倆 怎麼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.07,0:04:14.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小楓學姐快聽我說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.92,0:04:16.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的聲音——
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.27,0:04:17.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,換過來了！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.07,0:04:19.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我變成小葵——
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.72,0:04:21.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我變成日向——
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.39,0:04:22.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,換聲了！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.16,0:04:32.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小葵 日向 自己覺得奇怪的事情 有時並不是那麼怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.42,0:04:34.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.61,0:04:35.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.00,0:04:36.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.92,0:04:38.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.89,0:04:40.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聲音稍微有點…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.20,0:04:43.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感冒了？要吃藥嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.92,0:04:45.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.28,0:04:45.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.31,0:04:49.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽 我的聲音不奇怪嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.41,0:04:50.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？有嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.30,0:04:52.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.62,0:04:56.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天啊 日向踩到香蕉皮滑到了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.95,0:04:58.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這孩子真是的 沒受傷嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.22,0:04:59.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.48,0:05:05.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第7位 四少女漂流記
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.06,0:05:07.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然有點陰 但氣溫很高
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.17,0:05:10.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩水沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.37,0:05:12.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家游泳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.04,0:05:16.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小楓學姐 不脫衣服嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.73,0:05:17.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小葵你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.96,0:05:20.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個都害什麼羞呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.97,0:05:22.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日向！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.91,0:05:25.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危險！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.80,0:05:31.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熊吼——
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.08,0:05:34.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.93,0:05:41.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是哪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.18,0:05:43.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無人島啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.13,0:05:45.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子餓了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.95,0:05:46.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.13,0:05:47.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.27,0:05:54.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢馬君曲奇
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.81,0:05:57.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吃了！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.17,0:05:59.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不許一個人獨佔啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.30,0:06:00.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要吃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.35,0:06:02.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢馬是我的！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.23,0:06:04.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我先發現的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.25,0:06:05.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟那無關！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.10,0:06:14.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後 我們在島上長大成人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.23,0:06:16.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五年之後得到救援
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.76,0:06:23.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的野性獲得好評 出道成了女職業摔角手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.97,0:06:25.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看招日向
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.44,0:06:27.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從來沒這麼疼過！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.05,0:06:30.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來是4字形關節鎖！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.30,0:06:31.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.49,0:06:34.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,認輸？認輸？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.86,0:06:36.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熊！熊！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.95,0:06:41.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們先去預定好的本八合目的小屋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.52,0:06:42.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.39,0:06:43.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小葵學姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.94,0:06:45.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是高原反應
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.67,0:06:48.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們現在這觀察一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.55,0:06:50.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的話等會就跟上去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.04,0:06:54.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第5位 在太子館
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.19,0:07:02.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上好 我是聖德太子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.06,0:07:05.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖德…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.42,0:07:12.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 我以前騎馬來過這 太子館因此得名
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.30,0:07:15.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何啊 這馬不錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.77,0:07:18.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身子漆黑如烏鴉 四蹄潔白如新雪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.24,0:07:21.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是騎著它飛過來的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.96,0:07:24.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…咱今天就到這吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.02,0:07:28.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我腦袋可疼了 沒時間陪你閒扯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.94,0:07:30.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼說閒扯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.59,0:07:33.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看我可是聖德 聖德哦 太子那個聖德！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.24,0:07:35.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.10,0:07:37.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.64,0:07:40.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不信你試試 十個人一起跟我說我也能聽清哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.89,0:07:43.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧大家 Everybody say...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.29,0:07:46.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨 這位少女 等一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.20,0:07:48.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想回家…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.57,0:07:53.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼來到這裏…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.60,0:07:57.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TAI ZI先生好棒！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.60,0:07:58.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,登山少女
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.01,0:08:11.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不愧是小葵小姐 對歷史名人竟然如此冷淡！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.57,0:08:13.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太過獎啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.10,0:08:17.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來 山裏充滿邂逅呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.37,0:08:20.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們在谷川岳遇到了末明醬
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.58,0:08:24.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那之後 我們去群馬找末明醬
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.79,0:08:35.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒！竟然有蒸汽機車呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.62,0:08:38.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟是群馬 當然有蒸汽機車！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.86,0:08:48.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火車飛了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.06,0:08:51.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟是蒸汽機車 當然要飛向宇宙！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.59,0:08:53.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛去僊女座
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.20,0:08:56.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,入手性感的線條啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.67,0:09:03.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看啊 那是北十字星
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.02,0:09:05.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到奧利浦欣海岸了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.58,0:09:08.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走了好遠呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.68,0:09:09.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 那是！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.63,0:09:11.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可可娜醬！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.80,0:09:13.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小葵學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.57,0:09:17.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這件外衣是白頰鼯鼠的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.77,0:09:20.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 可可娜醬
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.52,0:09:27.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這之後 少女長成了大人！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.58,0:09:31.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只剩前三位了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.83,0:09:35.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的初戀情人米田君是第幾位呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.54,0:09:39.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才沒有呢 而且連長相都不記得了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.16,0:09:45.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第3位 冬天的禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.86,0:09:47.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖誕快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.66,0:09:50.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖誕快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.21,0:09:53.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來交換禮物吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.56,0:09:58.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那從我開始打開禮物吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.62,0:10:01.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凍果干什錦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.99,0:10:03.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我送的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.64,0:10:04.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.24,0:10:06.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來輪到我了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.40,0:10:08.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會有什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.39,0:10:12.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手套啊！這一定是小葵的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.45,0:10:13.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.48,0:10:15.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我一針一線織的呢 好好珍惜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.67,0:10:17.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好暖！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.22,0:10:20.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我收到的是什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.10,0:10:22.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是鐵鎖夾！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.30,0:10:23.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是小楓學姐送的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.86,0:10:25.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還能當鑰匙扣用呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.88,0:10:27.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.54,0:10:29.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我的禮物是可可娜醬送的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.34,0:10:33.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是曲奇呢 馴鹿版夢馬君
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.66,0:10:35.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝可可娜醬 都捨不得吃了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.23,0:10:39.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.92,0:10:41.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是聖誕老人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.66,0:10:42.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎們會呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.16,0:10:44.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.63,0:10:48.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖誕快樂 我是聖德老人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.29,0:10:55.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody say Merry Christmas————
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.43,0:11:04.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第2位 續 棉花糖少女可可娜醬
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.96,0:11:07.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏的話 有妖精也不奇怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.02,0:11:11.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道真的是妖精？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.69,0:11:20.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是天狗先生 埋伏嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.03,0:11:36.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天狗飛鏢！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.72,0:11:42.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕 今天穿了媽媽送我的鞋子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.85,0:11:46.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天狗迴旋鏢！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.31,0:11:56.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢馬
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.11,0:12:04.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你變強了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.70,0:12:09.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.38,0:12:11.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回來啦 可可娜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.54,0:12:14.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整條的鯛魚！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.54,0:12:16.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼日子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.88,0:12:18.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可喜可賀的日子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.26,0:12:20.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.93,0:12:23.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開動了！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.25,0:12:28.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老公 可可娜長大了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.21,0:12:34.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就差第1位了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.63,0:12:36.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第1位非那個片段莫屬
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.20,0:12:38.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.72,0:12:40.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,登山少女 BEST 10
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.91,0:12:42.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第1位是——
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.39,0:12:46.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回憶中的山峰 谷川岳
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.32,0:12:55.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘不掉的回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.41,0:13:04.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對 絕對不會忘記
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.34,0:13:11.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天狗大人 再見了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.56,0:13:13.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我絕對不會忘記天狗
