Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.41,0:13:27.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『山的女兒』殺青
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.75,0:13:29.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.44,0:13:31.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.12,0:13:33.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.58,0:13:35.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那個鏡頭特別好啊 小楓
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.78,0:13:38.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全拜山田導演所賜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.61,0:13:40.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還是那麼謙虛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.37,0:13:45.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可可娜醬 演技都超越劇本了呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.32,0:13:49.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次想演演主角呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.04,0:13:53.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 慶功會xx
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.28,0:13:57.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,KURO老師！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.09,0:13:59.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們演得太好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.30,0:14:01.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全合乎原作呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.21,0:14:03.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝老師
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.05,0:14:06.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師 今後的作品也要給我們啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.73,0:14:07.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一言為定
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.10,0:14:12.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備拍咯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.82,0:14:15.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茄子！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.61,0:14:21.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,登山少女 BEST 10就到這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.36,0:14:25.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家再會
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.85,0:14:42.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做了個好怪的夢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.12,0:14:44.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再睡會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.82,0:14:49.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天能看到怎樣的景色呢
